I see the following in /var/log/messages

Apr  2 18:56:43 web10 kernel: nfs_getpages: error 4

Upon this happening on a client if the file was locked it remains locked
which may be a problem elsewhere, however I believe nfs_getpages should
restart the system call that got interrupted.

Fix: 

I imagine the fix is somewhere in nfs_bio.c. I would imagine you just
check the error and if it's EINTR call it again but I don't know enough
to know if you can just recall the function...

